## 5. Design Principles
- **Modern & Dynamic**: High-end glassmorphism, neon accents (Cyan/Blue/Mint), deep dark background.
- **Data-Driven**: Every visual element must represent a specific data point from the reports.
- **Immersive**: Use subtle micro-animations to make the "Time Machine" feel alive.
